522
00:34:09,834 --> 00:34:11,750
Yeah, all right.

523
00:34:23,750 --> 00:34:25,041
Uh!

524
00:34:34,125 --> 00:34:36,667
Calvin, will you tell
your dad I had to go?

525
00:34:37,959 --> 00:34:41,041
Okay,
I'll see you later.
Bye.

526
00:34:54,542 --> 00:34:56,125
How?

