Let go!

555
00:36:28,709 --> 00:36:30,125
Don't scream at me. Let go!

556
00:36:30,208 --> 00:36:31,542
Look at me.

557
00:36:31,625 --> 00:36:34,375
Don't you dare hit me again.
Don't you hit me again.

558
00:36:34,458 --> 00:36:36,208
