562
00:37:03,625 --> 00:37:05,959
I'm sorry, Cal.

563
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:14,041
Cal, if you want to talk,
I'm downstairs, all right?

564
00:37:14,125 --> 00:37:16,375
I'm sorry.

565
00:37:16,458 --> 00:37:20,250
