and splashes you with water
when you're not looking.

611
00:40:28,667 --> 00:40:29,875
Do you like it?

612
00:40:29,959 --> 00:40:31,250
Mm-hmm. Yeah?

613
00:40:33,667 --> 00:40:37,125
Do you want to go outside
