or no?

614
00:40:37,208 --> 00:40:38,333
Can we?

615
00:40:39,875 --> 00:40:42,083
Mm-hmm.

616
00:40:42,166 --> 00:40:44,125
Okay.

617
00:40:52,625 --> 00:40:54,375
Whoo!

618
00:40:54,458 --> 00:40:57,709
