Right.

642
00:42:58,959 --> 00:43:03,375
You know,
see how it goes and...
Yeah.

643
00:43:03,458 --> 00:43:06,917
But, um, did you think
that, you know...
And I don't know, Kate.

644
00:43:07,000 --> 00:43:09,417
